title: #50 - Karl Jacobs Discusses MrBeast & Tells Secrets About the Dream SMP
itunes:title: #50 - Karl Jacobs Discusses MrBeast & Tells Secrets About the Dream SMP
description: One of the biggest personalities on YouTube, Twitter, and Twitch, Karl Jacobs comes to the 100 Thieves Cash App Compound for a new episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show. Beginning with how he became a prominent member of MrBeast's crew, Karl talks about the process behind MrBeast's biggest videos, whether or not he'd be leaving the crew to focus on his personal channel as well as his relationship with the other members of the group such as Chandler & Chris.
